{"tid":1883922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強與明星足球隊飯局影片流出　一哥：我做警察係學成龍方中信","createTime":"2020-02-17T09:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T13:50:43.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7543b101998fc256d8ece132c285e0a6a12f97","tid":1883922,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"今日網上流出一條影片，警務署署長鄧炳強聯同晨曦足球隊和明星足球隊齊齊食飯，席上鄧炳強更上台發言，台下藝人包括有成龍、曾志偉、譚詠麟、方中信、盧惠光、林國斌等人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4016278/org/ce2a32860241535d1dbccdcf5094b52f.jpg/h89K_hXjSgQkeZvgnHd_BTNNrWxdL6aTWLa_4Fi2v-A?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4016278%2Forg%2Fce2a32860241535d1dbccdcf5094b52f.jpg%2Fh89K_hXjSgQkeZvgnHd_BTNNrWxdL6aTWLa_4Fi2v-A%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=c051eabc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4016286/org/b2ebcce6268cc70023eaf605964c2082.jpg/Ylt8WtaRHuk1eGKRWpXU2ZhKjrgn7Wn5zDJYrcwyWK0?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4016286%2Forg%2Fb2ebcce6268cc70023eaf605964c2082.jpg%2FYlt8WtaRHuk1eGKRWpXU2ZhKjrgn7Wn5zDJYrcwyWK0%3Fv%3Dw640&h=ff8e677c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強指：「首先多謝晨曦同明星足球隊同我哋踢波食飯，同埋多謝警隊兄弟，因為佢哋真係好撐我。另外今日我好興奮，因為我見到好多偶像，由成龍大哥到Alan（譚詠麟）到志偉到阿Ben，全部都係我偶像，所以我心跳得好緊張。其實點解我區議會講嘢咁叻呢，因為就係聽志偉《開心字典》，其實我做警察呢係學成龍大哥同方中信，全部學你哋，我唔知點做警察，睇睇吓就識做。另外今日我其實好憎你（指譚詠麟），因為我老婆鍾意你多啲，無辦法，我都鍾意你。今日真係好多謝踢波嘅朋友同埋演藝嘅朋友，其實大家係老友，全部在心中唔使講嘢，只要你哋畀個手指公我哋，赴湯蹈火在所不辭。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4016290/org/b44760d0c39da5a9f81e3db00ca282be.jpg/bUtcmedOfAEC3hhDrp3fjfVH-dtVkS6Ni8u5iIvLuYg?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4016290%2Forg%2Fb44760d0c39da5a9f81e3db00ca282be.jpg%2FbUtcmedOfAEC3hhDrp3fjfVH-dtVkS6Ni8u5iIvLuYg%3Fv%3Dw640&h=3675ab0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4016292/org/32abb11f4e9b2e64effaf8d1fa654796.jpg/bnkRltuaA3nGaUTTTF6uKN0y_DfIYaXbGakLrhmpC64?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4016292%2Forg%2F32abb11f4e9b2e64effaf8d1fa654796.jpg%2FbnkRltuaA3nGaUTTTF6uKN0y_DfIYaXbGakLrhmpC64%3Fv%3Dw640&h=741a9d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成員大哥也有份在台上發言，更叫大家一起上台唱《朋友》，他說：「不管我們是哪一個階級、哪一層，我們都是朋友。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e214cfdb66f770df1c20a06.jpg/O21iUgRZ8TBPXV0t_gvF4OI88httcgWloYUGI6GFBiM?v=w1440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e214cfdb66f770df1c20a06.jpg%2FO21iUgRZ8TBPXV0t_gvF4OI88httcgWloYUGI6GFBiM%3Fv%3Dw1440&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d533a889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e214cfdb66f770df1c20a06.jpg/O21iUgRZ8TBPXV0t_gvF4OI88httcgWloYUGI6GFBiM?v=w1440</a><br />\n鄧炳強在中西區區議會上表達香港警方立場。"},{"pid":"d32f87a67ba14cc8bed21977e8e27ff1d6f96840","tid":1883922,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"明星足球隊 羅鈞滿 有CSi 口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1883785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1883785/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7a346c87f3156df7e573c3060c9504e48f51fc73","tid":1883922,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"302f887b8b457115d3fd17a419e86584bf3c7ac4","tid":1883922,"uid":293650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"集氣。。。中武漢肺炎。"},{"pid":"02ec1eff7a44f5e44634bbb6821ac60a6a71949c","tid":1883922,"uid":31094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"無間道原來係真"},{"pid":"8529044bcb5d8fb485b5864d91339eb3b2802065","tid":1883922,"uid":97551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"學做黑警<br />\n<br 